<div class="create-service account">
  <div class="container">
    <%= render "/home/left"%>

    <div class="right-create-service">
      <h1>Create Service</h1>
      <form action="create_process" method="post">
        <input name="authenticity_token" type="hidden" value="<%= form_authenticity_token %>" />

        <h3 class="language">Language &nbsp;<img src="/assets/my_account/circle_question_gray.png"></h3>
        <h5 class="language-select">EN &nbsp;&nbsp;<span>X</span></h5>

        <div class="popover-markup">
          <img src="/assets/my_account/circle_plus.png" class="trigger" data-original-title="" title="" aria-describedby="popover603483">
          <div class="content hide" style="top: 280px; left: 389px; display: block;">
            <p>English</p>
            <p>Spanish</p>
            <p>Vitnamese</p>
            <p>Chinese</p>
            <p>German</p>
            <p>Portuguese</p>
            <p>Japanese</p>
            <p>French</p>
            <p>Italian</p>
            <p>Korean</p>
            <p>Russian</p>
            <p>Malay</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        

        <input type="text" placeholder="service_name">
        <h3>Marketing Type</h3>
        <textarea type="text" placeholder="Service Detail" rows="4"></textarea>

        <h3>Cost</h3>
        <input type="radio" class="check"> Flat Rate
        <input type="radio" class="check"> Multiple Rate
        <input type="text" placeholder="$">

        

        <h3>Minimum Budget<input type="checkbox" class="check"></h3>
        <input type="text" placeholder="$">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Country" class="country-input">


        <img src="/assets/my_account/circle_question_gray.png" type="button" class="popover-hide country-q" data-container="body" data-toggle="popover" data-placement="top" data-content="This is your very own Campaign Monitor URL where you and your dlients will login to your account.">


        <img src="/assets/my_account/circle_plus.png" class="country-plus">

        <h3>[Optional] Attach Document <input type="checkbox" class="check"></h3>
        <input type="file">
        1. <input type="text" class="optional"> (주) 게임베리 회사소개.pdf
        <a href="#none">Delete</a><br>
        2. <input type="text" class="optional"> CPI Media Kit_2014.ppt
        <a href="#none">Delete</a><br>
        3. <input type="text" class="optional"> GameberryIntroduction.pdf
        <a href="#none">Delete</a><br>

        <br><br><br><br><br>
        <h2>Company Introduction</h2>
        <textarea type="text" placeholder="Company Introduction" name="company_name" rows="4"></textarea>
        <input type="file" name="upload_logo">

        <h5><input type="checkbox" class="check"> I have read and agree to the <span>Terms of Use</span> and <span>Privacy Policy</span></h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-a">Save</button>
        <br>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-b">Delete</button>

      </form>

      <p>
        I know you will not read full <span>terms.</span> But you should know at least these!<br><br>
        1. sdflsdjfiejlsdfkjmsdklfwfwefe<br><Br>
        3. 정글이 광고주로부터 수령하는 실수령 금액 (송금 수수료를 제외한) 중 <br>4.95%를 제외한 나머지 금액을 광고 매체에 지급한다.<Br><br>
        4. 대금 지급 일정 : 안전하고 투명한 거래를 위해 정글은 광고주에게는 <br>100% 선금으로 대금을 수령하고, 광고 매체 측에는 캠페인이 100% 정상적으로 <Br> 완료된 후에 대금을 지급한다.<br><Br>
        5. 캠페인이 정상적으로 완료되었다고 판단이 되면 (Campaign Result)
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>






